      <figcaption class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-3"><img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=120&q=80" alt=""><span><span class="block text-[14px] font-medium">Dana Russo</span><span class="block text-[12px] text-inkt/50">Founder, creative agency</span></span></figcaption>
